{
  "text": ") [CITATION_1] Riedl et al., 2012) . They withstand hypoxic conditions by curbing their oxygen consumption and exploiting anaerobic respiration, and individuals that are emersed can absorb oxygen from the air [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] .",
